OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776753489
OL,3,CLiquidated waste management firm fined
OL,4,C#1 after worker crushed by excavator
OL,6,FA Hampshire waste management company
OL,7,Fwhich went into liquidation after a
OL,8,Fworker was crushed by a 15-tonne
OL,9,Fexcavator has been fined #1.
OL,11,FThe worker, a 24-year-old man had both
OL,12,Flower legs amputated following the
OL,13,Fincident at R W Waste Limited at its
OL,14,Fyard in Shedfield on 7 November 2023.
OL,16,FThe excavator, which was operating in
OL,17,Fthe same yard, reversed over him as he
OL,18,Fwas sorting waste.
OL,20,FMr Parrott has been unable to return
OL,21,Fto work since.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
