PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776753489
OL,3,CLiquidated waste management firm fined
OL,4,C#1 after worker crushed by excavator
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that the
OL,8,Fcompany failed to protect workers and
OL,9,Fother visitors to the site.
OL,11,FThe company hadn't put in place
OL,12,Fsuitable arrangements to keep
OL,13,Fpedestrians safe while vehicles were
OL,14,Fmoving around the yard.
OL,16,FR W Waste Limited, of Botley Road,
OL,17,FShedfield, pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,18,FSection 2(1) and Section 3(1) of the
OL,19,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,20,F1974.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
