OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776753489
OL,3,CLiquidated waste management firm fined
OL,4,C#1 after worker crushed by excavator
OL,6,FAt Southampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,F16 April 2026 the court heard that the
OL,8,Fappropriate fine, after trial, would
OL,9,Fhave been #180,000, which was reduced
OL,10,Fto #120,000 to reflect the company's
OL,11,Fguilty plea.
OL,13,FHowever, as the company had gone into
OL,14,Fliquidation and was unable to pay, it
OL,15,Fwas ordered to pay a nominal fine of
OL,16,F#1.
OL,18,FNo order for costs was made for the
OL,19,Fsame reason.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
