PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776753489
OL,3,CLiquidated waste management firm fined
OL,4,C#1 after worker crushed by excavator
OL,6,FHSE Inspector Nicola Pinckney said:
OL,7,F"The failures of this company has left
OL,8,Fa young man with truly life-changing
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,F"He has not been able to work since.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, this type of accident
OL,14,Fis sadly not uncommon in this industry.
OL,16,F"After the incident, and following
OL,17,Fenforcement action taken by HSE, the
OL,18,Fcompany did introduce a number of
OL,19,Freadily available measures that
OL,20,Fsignificantly reduce the risk of this
OL,21,Fhappening again.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
